shared GetEntity = let
    // This function retrieves a table (Entity) from the given
    // workspaceName and dataflowName which are pre-defined
    // parameters 
    // Set the pWorkSpace and pDataFlow parameters before
    // invoking this function
    ReturnEntity = (pEntity as text) => let
        Source = PowerBI.Dataflows(null),
        UpperCaseWorkspace = Table.TransformColumns(Source, {{"workspaceName", each Text.Upper(Text.From(_)), type nullable text}}),
        Workspace = UpperCaseWorkspace{[workspaceName=Text.Upper(pWorkSpace)]}[Data],        
        UpperCaseDataflow = Table.TransformColumns(Workspace, {{"dataflowName", each Text.Upper(Text.From(_)), type nullable text}}),
        Dataflow = UpperCaseDataflow{[dataflowName=Text.Upper(pDataFlow)]}[Data],        
        UpperCaseEntity = Table.TransformColumns(Dataflow, {{"entity", each Text.Upper(Text.From(_)), type nullable text}}),
        Entity = UpperCaseEntity{[entity=Text.Upper(pEntity)]}[Data]
    in
        Entity
in
    ReturnEntity;
shared GetEntityFromWorkspace = let
    // This function retrieves a table (Entity) for the give
    // workspaceName and dataflowName which are variables
    // invoked in this function
    ReturnEntity = (pWorkSpace as text, pDataFlow as text, pEntity as text) => let
        Source = PowerBI.Dataflows(null),
        UpperCaseWorkspace = Table.TransformColumns(Source, {{"workspaceName", each Text.Upper(Text.From(_)), type nullable text}}),
        Workspace = UpperCaseWorkspace{[workspaceName=Text.Upper(pWorkSpace)]}[Data],        
        UpperCaseDataflow = Table.TransformColumns(Workspace, {{"dataflowName", each Text.Upper(Text.From(_)), type nullable text}}),
        Dataflow = UpperCaseDataflow{[dataflowName=Text.Upper(pDataFlow)]}[Data],        
        UpperCaseEntity = Table.TransformColumns(Dataflow, {{"entity", each Text.Upper(Text.From(_)), type nullable text}}),
        Entity = UpperCaseEntity{[entity=Text.Upper(pEntity)]}[Data]
    in
        Entity
in
    ReturnEntity;

[Description = "Coherent Fiscal Calendar.#(lf)Currently filtered to > 29th Sept. 2019"]
shared #"DIM_Fiscal Calendar" = let
/*
DIM_Fiscal Calendar is a modified view of the Fiscal Calendar where

A date filter has been applied so that only dates after pFiscalCalendarDateFilter are included
Additional columns have been added Cal_Year_ofCW, Cal_Year_ofCW_Short
*/
    FiscalCalendarData = GetEntity("Fiscal Calendar Days"),
    TransformColumnTypes = Table.TransformColumnTypes(FiscalCalendarData,{{"Calendar Day", type date}, {"Week Start Date", type date}, {"Week End Date", type date}, {"Period Start Date", type date}, {"Period End Date", type date}, {"Quarter Start Date", type date}, {"Quarter End Date", type date}, {"Year Start Date", type date}, {"Year End Date", type date}, {"Fiscal Week No", Int64.Type}, {"Fiscal Month Week No", Int64.Type}, {"Fiscal Qtr Week No", Int64.Type}, {"Period Year", Int64.Type}, {"Quarter No", Int64.Type}, {"Period No", Int64.Type}, {"Fiscal Day", Int64.Type}, {"FC_PERIOD_ID", Int64.Type}, {"FC_QUARTER_ID", Int64.Type}, {"FC_WEEK_ID", Int64.Type}, {"FC_YEAR_OFFSET", Int64.Type}, {"FC_QUARTER_OFFSET", Int64.Type}, {"FC_PERIOD_OFFSET", Int64.Type}, {"FC_WEEK_OFFSET", Int64.Type}, {"FC_DAYS_OFFSET", Int64.Type}, {"CALENDAR_YEAR", Int64.Type}, {"CALENDAR_MONTH", Int64.Type}, {"CALENDAR_ISO_WEEK", Int64.Type}, {"CALENDAR_US_WEEK", Int64.Type}, {"DAY_OF_WEEK", Int64.Type}, {"WORKING_DAY_FLAG", Int64.Type}, {"FISCAL_WEEK_INDICATOR_SORT", Int64.Type}, {"FISCAL_MONTH_INDICATOR_SORT", Int64.Type}, {"FISCAL_QUARTER_INDICATOR_SORT", Int64.Type}, {"FISCAL_YEAR_INDICATOR_SORT", Int64.Type}}),
    //Gets all dates from the year offset given by pFiscalCalendarDateFilter (default is set as 3 years)
    SelectAllRowsAfterThisDate = 
    let
        GetLastNYearsOfData = Table.AddColumn(TransformColumnTypes, "PreviousNYears", each Date.IsInPreviousNYears([Calendar Day], pFiscalCalendarDateFilter)),
        GetCurrentYearsData = Table.AddColumn(GetLastNYearsOfData, "CurrentFutureYears", each [Calendar Day] >= Date.From(Date.StartOfYear(DateTime.FixedLocalNow()))),
        SelectTheFilteredRows = Table.SelectRows(GetCurrentYearsData, each List.AnyTrue({[PreviousNYears], [CurrentFutureYears]})),
        ReturnFinalValue = Table.RemoveColumns(SelectTheFilteredRows,{"PreviousNYears", "CurrentFutureYears"})
    in
        ReturnFinalValue,
    RenameFiscalWeekColumns = Table.RenameColumns(SelectAllRowsAfterThisDate,{{"Fiscal Week", "Fiscal Year Week"}, {"Fiscal Year Week", "Fiscal Week"}}),
    AddStartOfWeekCOlumn = Table.AddColumn(RenameFiscalWeekColumns, "Start of Week", each Date.StartOfWeek([Calendar Day]), type date),
    #"Inserted Year" = Table.AddColumn(AddStartOfWeekCOlumn, "Cal_Year_ofCW", each Date.Year([Start of Week]), Int64.Type),
    GetThe2DigitValueOfYear = Table.AddColumn(#"Inserted Year", "Cal_Year_ofCW_Short", each Text.End(Text.From([Cal_Year_ofCW]), 2), type number),
    /*
    Returns a column with the Year and CW combined and prefixes included
    eg. Year = 2022 and CW = 26 then value returned is "Y22_CW26"
    */
    SetYearAndCWColumn = let 
        TextCalendarYear = Table.AddColumn(GetThe2DigitValueOfYear, "TextCalendarYear", each "Y" & Text.End(Text.From([Cal_Year_ofCW]), 2), type number),
        TextCalendarISOWeek = Table.AddColumn(TextCalendarYear, "TextCalendarISOWeek", each "_CW" & Text.End(Text.From([CALENDAR_ISO_WEEK]), 2), type number),
        CombineYearAndISOWeek = Table.AddColumn(TextCalendarISOWeek, "CALENDAR_Year_CWiso", each Text.Combine({[TextCalendarYear], Text.From([TextCalendarISOWeek])}), type text),
        ReturnCalendarYearCWIso = Table.RemoveColumns(CombineYearAndISOWeek,{"TextCalendarYear", "TextCalendarISOWeek"})
        in ReturnCalendarYearCWIso,
    /*
    Returns a column with the Year x 100 and CW added together
    eg. Year = 2024 and CW = 26 then value returned is 202426
    */
    SetCalYearAndCWIDColumn = let
    MultiplyCalYearCWBy100 = Table.AddColumn(SetYearAndCWColumn, "Cal_Year_ofCWx100", each [Cal_Year_ofCW] * 100, type number),
    AddtheWeekToTheMultipliedValue = Table.AddColumn(MultiplyCalYearCWBy100, "Cal_Year_CWiso_ID", each [Cal_Year_ofCWx100] + [CALENDAR_ISO_WEEK], type number),
    TransformTheColumnTypes = Table.TransformColumnTypes(AddtheWeekToTheMultipliedValue,{{"Cal_Year_CWiso_ID", Int64.Type}, {"Cal_Year_ofCWx100", Int64.Type}, {"Cal_Year_ofCW_Short", Int64.Type}}),
    ReturnCalYearId = Table.RemoveColumns(TransformTheColumnTypes,{"Cal_Year_ofCWx100"})
    in 
        ReturnCalYearId,
    AddPrefixToCalendarISOWeek = Table.AddColumn(SetCalYearAndCWIDColumn, "Cal_CW", each "CW" & Text.From([CALENDAR_ISO_WEEK]), type text),
    KeepColumns = Table.SelectColumns(AddPrefixToCalendarISOWeek,{"Period Set Name", "Calendar Day", "Fiscal Year Week", "Fiscal Week", "FISCAL_WEEK_DISP", "FISCAL_MONTH_SORT_VALUE", "FISCAL_QUARTER_DISP", "Fiscal Week No", "Fiscal Month Week No", "FISCAL_QTR_WEEK", "Fiscal Qtr Week No", "GL Period", "PQ_LAST_GL_PERIOD", "Period Year", "Fiscal Year", "Quarter No", "Fiscal Quarter", "Fiscal Year Quarter", "PRIOR_FYFQ", "PERIOD_NAME", "Period No", "Fiscal Day", "Week Start Date", "Week End Date", "Period Start Date", "Period End Date", "Quarter Start Date", "Quarter End Date", "Year Start Date", "Year End Date", "Fiscal Period Month", "FC_PERIOD_ID", "FC_QUARTER_ID", "FC_WEEK_ID", "FC_YEAR_OFFSET", "FC_QUARTER_OFFSET", "FC_PERIOD_OFFSET", "FC_WEEK_OFFSET", "FC_DAYS_OFFSET", "FC_HALF", "Next Quarter First Fiscal Week", "Prior Qtr Last Fiscal Week", "CALENDAR_YEAR", "CALENDAR_MONTH", "CALENDAR_YEARMONTHID", "CALENDAR_MONTHNAME", "CALENDAR_MONTHNAMESHORT", "CALENDAR_ISO_WEEK", "CALENDAR_US_WEEK", "CALENDAR_YEAR_SHORT", "CALENDAR_MTH_YEAR", "DAY_NAME", "DAY_OF_WEEK", "WORKING_DAY_FLAG", "CQ_LAST_FISCAL_WEEK", "Row Creation Date", "Week End Flag", "Month End Flag", "Quarter End Flag", "Year End Flag", "FISCAL_WEEK_INDICATOR", "FISCAL_WEEK_INDICATOR_SORT", "FISCAL_MONTH_INDICATOR", "FISCAL_MONTH_INDICATOR_SORT", "FISCAL_QUARTER_INDICATOR", "FISCAL_QUARTER_INDICATOR_SORT", "FISCAL_YEAR_INDICATOR", "FISCAL_YEAR_INDICATOR_SORT", "Refresh Date", "Start of Week", "Cal_Year_ofCW", "Cal_Year_ofCW_Short", "CALENDAR_Year_CWiso", "Cal_Year_CWiso_ID", "Cal_CW"})
in
    KeepColumns;
